CustomField.description: The Domestic Ultimate is the highest entity within an organization and is identified by a nine-digit Domestic Ultimate D-U-N-S Number. All companies that are part of the same corporate structure as the Domestic Ultimate are identified by the same Domestic Ultimate D-U-N-S Number.
